17 Hours Ago    “The President condoles with family members, government and people of Katsina State, and all associates of the former President of NPAN, especially the media industry, on the loss, describing him as greatly admired and respected. “President Buhari believes the demise of the publisher and businessman has created a huge gap as Funtua consistently stood by him in his political journey."